data.text:
Blogg by : IRFAN-UL-HAQ

The launch event was organized by Catwalk Productions and PR handled by Catalyst PR & Marketing. The glamorous evening was attended by crème de la crème of fashion including Saba Ansari, Sanam Chaudhry, Ubaid Sheikh, Nomi Ansari, Bunto Kazmi, Seemi Tapal, Amna Isani, Farhan, Farishte Aslam, Shehrnaz Husain, Tapu Javeri, Zahir Rahmatullah, Noorain, Neelo, Pinky Navaid and more.

Once again the dynamic duo SanaSafinaz has put together something extraordinary and this time around in form of a complete sartorial solution! The one stop shop collection comprises of everything from less formal attire stitched lawn suits, to evening wear jumpsuits, silk tunics with crystal embellishments and an array of sandals and accessories which makes the entire collection quite versatile.

The aura of luxury and elegance can be felt as soon as one enters the store. This store is sartorial dream come true for all the fashion savvy women out there! Not only does it entail a wide range of clothing line available in variegated colors, but also the accessories and shoes which compliments them. The price range starts from Rs. 3000 for the lawn suits, Rs. 4200 for the evening wear & 15000 for the Chikan Kari and goes up to where the sky’s the limit.

“The label of the designer duo Sana Safinaz has been long synonymous with graceful elegant chic styles. The opening of the retail stores has been a dream for us and has been in works for over a year. Our mission was to be able to create a high street brand which would cater to young girls, a working girl and women. It will be a one stop shop where one can come in and have the option to buy a complete outfit down to the very last detail. We have chappals, evening sandals, accessories, stitched lawn and evening outfits. The options are endless. We hope you enjoy wearing them as much as we have enjoyed the process of designing each item for you.” comments the duo

The event featured renowned models including Areeba, Sara Khan, Sehrish, Sidra Sajid, Abeer, Saba Sikander, Manaal, Nadia Hussain, Fauzia, Dania, Noor & Neha who were adorned in beautiful outfits by SanaSafinaz.
